" of the parameter. Translates to ``inversesqrt(x)`` in the Godot Shader "
"Language."
msgstr ""

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_visualshadernodefloatfunc.rst:151
msgid ""
