"``x`` (i.e. ``1 / x``)."
msgstr ""

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_visualshadernodefloatfunc.rst:157
msgid ""
"**FUNC_ROUNDEVEN** = **29** --- Finds the nearest even integer to the "
"parameter. Translates to ``roundEven(x)`` in the Godot Shader Language."
msgstr ""

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_visualshadernodefloatfunc.rst:159
msgid ""
"**FUNC_TRUNC** = **30** --- Returns a value equal to the nearest integer "
"to ``x`` whose absolute value is not larger than the absolute value of "
"``x``. Translates to ``trunc(x)`` in the Godot Shader Language."
msgstr ""

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_visualshadernodefloatfunc.rst:161
msgid ""
"**FUNC_ONEMINUS** = **31** --- Subtracts scalar ``x`` from 1 (i.e. ``1 - "
"x``)."
msgstr ""

